男女警員</span></strong>前往酒吧消遺之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117bcbb28e40e0bcf6b5e76cb3b76530df5626ac","tid":2289363,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T08:14:14.000Z","msg":"消息指，兩名警務人員涉嫌強姦被捕。據了解，早前有兩男兩女到一間酒吧消遣，其中一名女性其後離開，獨留兩男一女。該三人之後前往一間酒店，事後女子報稱被強姦。警方經調查後，拘捕案中兩名男子，涉嫌強姦。消息指，他們為警務人員，分別是<strong><span class=\"red\">機動部隊人員</span></strong>及<strong><span class=\"red\">刑事調查隊探員</span></strong>。案件交由西九龍總區重案組跟進，現正調查案件詳情。<br />\n<br />\n01唔貼link"},{"pid":"aca4b126b611e3038cae7c806600cb8a387aaacf","tid":2289363,"uid":173191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T08:15:57.000Z","msg":"被姦果個係咪狗乸嚟？"},{"pid":"0f41931d117396826c09cbe8888f79bc790c7e0d","tid":2289363,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T08:17:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20191109/1536pix/1573313163_c6f7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20191109%2F1536pix%2F1573313163_c6f7.png&h=fed786fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/f56d6f/f/800x0/https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191016/720pix/1571215098_42e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2Ff56d6f%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191016%2F720pix%2F1571215098_42e9.jpg&h=d272aef5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1760443/org/0205877dff68fe26be6b6f60fb47ea8d.jpg/uk05P2En4vHG8cFjsGnRxzPT_iqZlIqwj_HFuo_xxbo?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1760443%2Forg%2F0205877dff68fe26be6b6f60fb47ea8d.jpg%2Fuk05P2En4vHG8cFjsGnRxzPT_iqZlIqwj_HFuo_xxbo%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=fabce4be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qySjATw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=htt